      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "This project introduces \u201CSpeak Up!\u201D, an immersive Virtual Reality
    (VR) learning application designed to improve English conversational skills through
    interactive, real-life practice scenarios.\n\nThis project features generative
    AI (ChatGPT-powered NPCs), NPC behaviours, speech-to-text transcription, text-to-speech
    voices and multi-agent conversational systems. These features allow learners
    to engage in natural conversations with multiple AI-driven characters, experience
    social interaction settings like classrooms , public speaking venue stage and
    kopitiam, and receive personalized language feedback in an engaging and interactive
    environment.\n\nThis VR Application is developed by Eddie Ooi Wei Kit."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 457322e28941d8247aff37eb8443eb92, type: 2}
